div.head: Description of changes for 2012.09
div.p: This is the first public version of this text. It is a first draft of an edited text copy from a diplomatic transcription of the St. Victor manuscript witness. It awaits corrections and additions that arise from comparison of the other manuscript witnesses. Citations, cross-references, and a critical apparatus all still need to be added"
